00:22:35,067 --> 00:22:37,167
Go on. Tell her.

268
00:22:39,867 --> 00:22:41,000
So, listen.

269
00:22:43,500 --> 00:22:44,333
I...

270
00:22:46,000 --> 00:22:47,067
I love...

271
00:22:48,733 --> 00:22:49,900
Michaela Moon Rabbit.

272
00:22:52,367 --> 00:22:53,500
Thanks.

273
00:22:54,633 --> 00:22:55,600
I love...

274
00:22:57,000 --> 00:22:57,867
you.

275
00:22:59,567 --> 00:23:01,100
Chiyomi Horikiri.

276
00:23:01,167 --> 00:23:02,367
Yes.

