00:23:26,100 --> 00:23:31,633
But I had to tell you
how I feel about you.

281
00:23:33,667 --> 00:23:35,733
I wanna nominate myself.

282
00:23:38,333 --> 00:23:41,133
So, I'm not gonna rush you.

283
00:23:41,800 --> 00:23:42,800
Riku?

284
00:23:43,667 --> 00:23:46,600
I'll walk away if there's someone.

285
00:23:47,333 --> 00:23:51,000
But if there isn't someone else...

286
00:23:53,667 --> 00:23:57,300
I'll always be waiting for you
to choose me.

287
00:23:59,033 --> 00:24:02,033
Riku is such a great guy.

288
00:24:02,267 --> 00:24:05,433
He's fun to talk to. He's sweet.

289
00:24:05,933 --> 00:24:10,633
And he likes me,
which means he clearly has great taste.

290
00:24:21,567 --> 00:24:22,400
Shoot.

291
00:24:35,700 --> 00:24:39,100
The rain... I forgot my umbrella.

292
00:25:41,867 --> 00:25:44,467
Are you studying for med school?

293
00:26:10,300 --> 00:26:11,200
Why?

294
00:26:14,667 --> 00:26:16,933
Why does it make me cry?

295
00:26:27,267 --> 00:26:29,867
I love you, Chiyomi.

296
00:26:29,933 --> 00:26:30,867
I love you.

297
00:26:44,233 --> 00:26:45,067
I'm...

298
00:26:49,767 --> 00:26:52,300
I'm in love with Minami...

299
00:26:57,533 --> 00:26:58,700
all this time...

300
00:27:35,667 --> 00:27:37,100
You're going to Tokyo?

301
00:27:37,800 --> 00:27:39,400
Explain yourself.

302
00:27:39,467 --> 00:27:42,800
My favorite dance team
is having an audition.

303
00:27:43,700 --> 00:27:48,267
But you don't have to go now,
you have your exams this year.

304
00:27:48,367 --> 00:27:51,000
But I wanna go now. I wanna go.

305
00:27:51,067 --> 00:27:52,567
You're not going.

306
00:27:52,733 --> 00:27:56,267
You're too young to go
to Tokyo all by yourself.

307
00:27:56,400 --> 00:27:59,767
I agree. Your silly dance team can wait.

308
00:27:59,833 --> 00:28:01,800
"Silly dance team"?

309
00:28:02,467 --> 00:28:04,900
Well, I'm not going to college.

310
00:28:05,967 --> 00:28:07,267
I won't take the exams.

311
00:28:07,333 --> 00:28:11,900
I know what I want,
and college is just a waste of time.

312
00:28:12,367 --> 00:28:17,967
Listen to yourself. You got into
a decent high school, don't waste it.

313
00:28:18,033 --> 00:28:20,133
Your mom is right.

314
00:28:20,200 --> 00:28:21,867
You'll regret this later.

315
00:28:22,300 --> 00:28:25,500
Why are you two suddenly teaming up?

316
00:28:25,867 --> 00:28:28,533
You never listened to your mom?

317
00:28:28,600 --> 00:28:29,667
What are you saying?

318
00:28:29,733 --> 00:28:32,233
I know you had a shotgun wedding!

319
00:28:35,333 --> 00:28:36,400
Honey...

320
00:28:40,500 --> 00:28:43,333
Chiyomi. We're not done here.

321
00:28:49,333 --> 00:28:52,200
The lightning is getting closer.

322
00:28:54,467 --> 00:28:55,400
What?

323
00:28:58,000 --> 00:28:59,100
Chiyomi?

324
00:29:13,700 --> 00:29:16,633
BUOY ME A BOTTLE OF SOY SAUCE. MOM

325
00:29:17,100 --> 00:29:19,467
Why is she making me run errands?

326
00:29:20,000 --> 00:29:22,267
It's "buy," not "buoy."

327
00:29:31,767 --> 00:29:32,600
Are you okay?

328
00:29:55,633 --> 00:30:00,033
Are you studying for med school?

329
00:30:01,167 --> 00:30:02,000
Yeah.

330
00:30:02,733 --> 00:30:05,900
I don't mean to pry,
but can you afford it?

331
00:30:06,633 --> 00:30:09,000
Your mother is single, right?

332
00:30:12,467 --> 00:30:14,733
Why don't you ask my father?

333
00:30:16,167 --> 00:30:19,367
I'm sure he'll help you find a solution.

334
00:30:43,500 --> 00:30:44,633
Minami.

335
00:30:47,733 --> 00:30:48,567
What?

336
00:30:58,467 --> 00:30:59,400
What do you want?

337
00:31:00,800 --> 00:31:02,133
I'm going home.

338
00:31:03,600 --> 00:31:04,900
Why do you ignore me?

339
00:31:10,100 --> 00:31:12,233
I said, why do you ignore me?

340
00:31:14,867 --> 00:31:17,033
-No, I'm not.
-Yes, you are.

341
00:31:20,433 --> 00:31:22,633
You're nice to Sayori.

342
00:31:25,533 --> 00:31:28,100
Were you with her this whole time?

343
00:31:28,700 --> 00:31:30,767
Are you gonna date her?

344
00:31:31,500 --> 00:31:34,367
Please. It has nothing to do with you.

345
00:31:36,600 --> 00:31:37,767
You're right.

346
00:31:39,800 --> 00:31:41,700
I'm nothing to you.

347
00:31:45,367 --> 00:31:47,567
Sorry. I didn't mean to...

348
00:31:49,867 --> 00:31:51,067
Damn.

349
00:31:53,933 --> 00:31:57,267
You need to stop showing up
everywhere I go.

350
00:31:57,867 --> 00:31:59,500
When did I ever?

351
00:31:59,600 --> 00:32:02,100
Earlier, when I was with Sayori.

352
00:32:03,567 --> 00:32:06,567
-I didn't plan it.
-Not that I care.

353
00:32:08,367 --> 00:32:11,500
I'm out here because
I fought with my parents.

354
00:32:12,000 --> 00:32:12,833
A fight?

355
00:32:13,367 --> 00:32:16,367
They're mad at me
for not wanting to college.

356
00:32:17,533 --> 00:32:18,800
You're not?

357
00:32:18,867 --> 00:32:20,433
I have my goals.

358
00:32:21,600 --> 00:32:24,867
They wouldn't hear me out.

359
00:32:30,900 --> 00:32:32,467
You must be joking.

360
00:32:36,200 --> 00:32:38,200
You're a spoiled brat.

361
00:32:38,967 --> 00:32:39,800
What?

362
00:32:43,367 --> 00:32:46,233
What would you say that? It hurts.

363
00:32:46,967 --> 00:32:49,233
We used to be best friends.

364
00:32:50,267 --> 00:32:51,367
Why?

365
00:32:57,167 --> 00:32:58,367
Don't you get it?

366
00:33:01,233 --> 00:33:03,300
I can't stand you anymore.

367
00:33:39,733 --> 00:33:40,600
Hey!

368
00:33:45,500 --> 00:33:46,600
Hold on!

369
00:33:47,300 --> 00:33:48,967
Wait!

370
00:34:16,300 --> 00:34:17,633
This place...

371
00:34:29,000 --> 00:34:31,633
Where is she? Her phone is dead.

372
00:34:31,700 --> 00:34:35,967
I thought she'd come home after my text.

373
00:34:36,067 --> 00:34:37,100
Let's go find her.

374
00:34:37,167 --> 00:34:39,700
-A storm's outside.
-That's why we go.

375
00:34:39,800 --> 00:34:42,233
Can you two chill out?

376
00:34:44,267 --> 00:34:46,033
Chiyomi. She's home.

377
00:34:51,000 --> 00:34:53,733
-Hey, Sakaizawa.
-Is Chiyomi home?

378
00:34:53,800 --> 00:34:54,633
No, why?

379
00:34:54,700 --> 00:34:58,533
Just as I thought. I saw her at the park.

380
00:34:59,000 --> 00:35:00,900
Officer, he slapped her.

381
00:35:01,000 --> 00:35:02,333
Stop that.

382
00:35:02,467 --> 00:35:05,500
She was in tears. I'm gonna arrest you.

383
00:35:05,567 --> 00:35:06,567
Arrest him.

384
00:35:06,633 --> 00:35:10,933
Stop the nonsense. Now take me to her.

385
00:35:11,600 --> 00:35:12,433
My jacket.

386
00:35:13,300 --> 00:35:14,233
Dad, shoes.

387
00:35:17,000 --> 00:35:18,200
Come on.

388
00:35:18,967 --> 00:35:20,200
Be careful.

389
00:35:27,933 --> 00:35:30,700
It's getting worse.

390
00:35:41,600 --> 00:35:44,967
No way. Come on back.

391
00:36:24,500 --> 00:36:25,867
Wait.

392
00:36:26,900 --> 00:36:27,967
Shunichi...

393
00:36:28,067 --> 00:36:30,033
-Don't go.
-Shunichi.

394
00:36:31,867 --> 00:36:32,700
I'm so sorry.

395
00:36:37,667 --> 00:36:39,100
I hate you!

396
00:36:53,033 --> 00:36:54,767
Shunichi, let's go inside.

397
00:37:17,800 --> 00:37:18,867
Bye, Mom.

398
00:37:29,233 --> 00:37:30,067
Hey.

399
00:38:03,067 --> 00:38:04,300
Don't you get it?

400
00:38:07,100 --> 00:38:09,133
I can't stand you anymore.

401
00:38:13,167 --> 00:38:16,200
What happened to us?

402
00:38:18,000 --> 00:38:20,933
We used to be best friends.

403
00:38:30,367 --> 00:38:32,967
I wanna go back to when it used to be...

404
00:38:36,133 --> 00:38:38,533
back to when we were little once again...

405
00:38:39,533 --> 00:38:41,067
Minami...

406
00:38:52,867 --> 00:38:53,700
Why?

407
00:38:55,333 --> 00:38:58,300
What would you say that? It hurts.

408
00:38:58,967 --> 00:39:01,300
We used to be best friends.

409
00:39:02,267 --> 00:39:03,433
Why?

410
00:40:08,167 --> 00:40:09,733
What happened?

411
00:40:35,100 --> 00:40:38,300
I turned into a One Inch Princess?

412
00:40:51,267 --> 00:40:52,300
No...

413
00:40:54,233 --> 00:40:56,733
No way!

414
00:43:02,100 --> 00:43:03,067
Chiyomi?

415
00:43:03,133 --> 00:43:04,700
NEXT EPISODE
EP. 02 "UNDER THE SAME ROOF?!"

416
00:43:04,767 --> 00:43:06,433
I'm over here, Minami.

417
00:43:07,500 --> 00:43:09,700
Chiyomi's gone missing?

418
00:43:09,767 --> 00:43:12,900
Just between you and me,
I suspect she eloped.

419
00:43:14,833 --> 00:43:17,800
They're gonna think I've been kidnapped.

420
00:43:21,500 --> 00:43:23,667
There is someone suspicious...

421
00:43:24,167 --> 00:43:25,500
right here among us.

422
00:43:27,867 --> 00:43:29,367
This bathtub is perfect for me.

423
